*HOW to use this package
1. cd to src and compile the code.
    cd src; make clean; make
2. You would see in lib(libasdf.a) and include(*.mod) files

*INTERFACE
1. read_asdf_file(...)
  see details in src/asdf_read_subs.f90
2. write_asf_file(...)
  see details in src/asdf_write_subs.f90

*Depandancy
1. adios
2. mpi


